what ip are you putting in? try 127.0.0.1 if that dosent work try 128.0.0.1 if that dosent work use localhost and if that dosent work, go down to start>run and type cmd
when it comes up type ipconfig and see what your ip adress is. and try that. also try your default gateway. if none of those work, your computer is fucked up.
